messages.message: We should rethink removing the heuristic classifier - it is part of solutions that we just put into production at Rocket this week.  Also it is being leveraged as a secondary classification mechanism when forms are structured and simple but vary  in a set consistent manner like - the heading consistently has a different name.

Thanks for the feedback, and if you have any additional context, can you add it to the https://instabase.atlassian.net/jira/polaris/projects/PFR/ideas?selectedIssue=PFR-963

others have asked the same question - let me respond in the PFR
